{"tid":972174,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"2019弱智無腦集合區","createTime":"2019-01-07T08:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T07:47:50.000Z","uid":25343,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60642a5b857f286b9fd3ac1fdd5ff28021b9d0e4","tid":972174,"uid":25343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"內有絲打有巴打，但全部都無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以谷聚唔會有用腦既活動，大多數都係食野、食野同食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔排除會有其他活動，睇admin心情，即興出聚都會<br />\n由於admin好友善，所以唔駛驚入黎無話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n填表就入得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/mgTfm4uQi7nwXQWe2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FmgTfm4uQi7nwXQWe2&d=eJNfJf4F4gWZ4jv3F0VDuQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=c8be8f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/mgTfm4uQi7nwXQWe2</a>"},{"pid":"f4bdf0ac5819fb0a4958e756ae910cc9ae82f3dc","tid":972174,"uid":25343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad138a5ad9f9529080592ec70a48f3387f5462e0","tid":972174,"uid":25343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535748fcdf9bb3ccfd698f4c0e9d17c91d046bd9","tid":972174,"uid":25343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2be6f8925dfd7cf535696fc3f9b492340ba9fa1","tid":972174,"uid":25343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:51:07.000